job.title: NIT Silchar Superintendent  Recruitment  2021  Apply offline for 55 Vacancies in Assam
job.body:
Total Vacancies: 55

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Superintendent

Description

Latest Central Government Jobs for graduates have been published by the National Institute of Technology for Superintendent vacancies in Assam. If you are searching for a government job in Assam then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Superintendent, from 28.05.2021, and till 02.07.2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Assam and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • No information about application fee

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for a Superintendent  in NIT, your Graduation must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 28.05.2021
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 02.07.2021

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 40 years old. 

NIT Superintendent Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is as per norms

How to apply for NIT Silchar Superintendent Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly download the application form there and easily start the application process of the Superintendent. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of NIT  and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by NIT 
  • Print out the application form
  • Fill up the details asked in the application form by blue or black pen
  • Now send this application form to the address mentioned in the official notification
